text.section:
An action on one of the following specialties shall be filed within 12 years after the cause of action accrues, or within 12 years from the date of the death of the last to die of the principal debtor or creditor, whichever is sooner:
Promissory note or other instrument under seal;
Bond except a public officer's bond;
Judgment;
Recognizance;
Contract under seal; or
Any other specialty.
